{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880444199,"sessionID":"ses_28547c854ffeAQCMC8DFjy0NXr","part":{"id":"prt_d7ab918f7001ysCx0ipEteOQB3","messageID":"msg_d7ab90403001lJa9Py6juWgkB3","sessionID":"ses_28547c854ffeAQCMC8DFjy0NXr","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-e8ee3066568c4737a5dd4c8fa61ab79c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/python-sdk/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/python-sdk/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-029: SDK HTTP 底层客户端 — Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: The SDK HTTP 底层客户端 provides the foundational HTTP client infrastructure for the AgentCube Python SDK, enabling communication with the Workload Manager (control plane) and Router (data plane) for Code Interpreter and Agent Runtime services.\n6: \n7: **Module:** `sdk-python`  \n8: **Language:** Python  \n9: **Source Root:** `/tmp/agentcube-ref/sdk-python/`  \n10: **Size:** M\n11: \n12: ## Architecture\n13: \n14: ### Components\n15: \n16: | Component | Location | Responsibility |\n17: |-----------|----------|----------------|\n18: | `create_session` | `agentcube/utils/http.py` | Creates pooled requests.Session with HTTPAdapter |\n19: | `read_token_from_file` | `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | Reads authentication token from file |\n20: | `get_logger` | `agentcube/utils/log.py` | Provides configured logger instances |\n21: | `ControlPlaneClient` | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | HTTP client for Workload Manager API |\n22: | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | HTTP client for Code Interpreter Router API |\n23: | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` | `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | HTTP client for Agent Runtime Router API |\n24: | `CodeInterpreterClient` | `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | High-level Code Interpreter client |\n25: | `AgentRuntimeClient` | `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | High-level Agent Runtime client |\n26: \n27: ### Data Flow\n28: \n29: ```\n30: Control Plane Flow:\n31: ControlPlaneClient → requests.Session → Workload Manager API\n32:                        ↓\n33:                   Connection Pooling\n34:                   HTTPAdapter (http/https)\n35: \n36: Data Plane Flow (Code Interpreter):\n37: CodeInterpreterClient → CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient → requests.Session → Router API\n38:                                                            ↓\n39:                                                       Connection Pooling\n40:                                                       HTTPAdapter (http/https)\n41: \n42: Data Plane Flow (Agent Runtime):\n43: AgentRuntimeClient → AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient → requests.Session → Router API\n44:                                                          ↓\n45:                                                     Connection Pooling\n46:                                                     HTTPAdapter (http/https)\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ## Package Structure\n50: \n51: ```\n52: agentcube-sdk/\n53: ├── pyproject.toml                    # Package metadata and dependencies\n54: ├── agentcube/\n55: │   ├── __init__.py                   # Public API exports\n56: │   ├── code_interpreter.py           # CodeInterpreterClient\n57: │   ├── agent_runtime.py              # AgentRuntimeClient\n58: │   ├── exceptions.py                 # Exception hierarchy\n59: │   ├── clients/\n60: │   │   ├── __init__.py              # Client re-exports\n61: │   │   ├── control_plane.py         # ControlPlaneClient\n62: │   │   ├── code_interpreter_data_plane.py  # CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\n63: │   │   └── agent_runtime_data_plane.py     # AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n64: │   └── utils/\n65: │       ├── __init__.py              # Module marker\n66: │       ├── http.py                  # create_session\n67: │       ├── utils.py                 # read_token_from_file\n68: │       └── log.py                   # get_logger\n69: ```\n70: \n71: ## Detailed Implementation\n72: \n73: ### 1. HTTP Session Management (`agentcube/utils/http.py`)\n74: \n75: ```python\n76: def create_session(\n77:     pool_connections: int = 10,\n78:     pool_maxsize: int = 10,\n79: ) -> requests.Session:\n80:     \"\"\"Create a requests.Session with connection pooling.\n81: \n82:     Args:\n83:         pool_connections: Number of connection pools to cache\n84:         pool_maxsize: Maximum number of connections in pool\n85: \n86:     Returns:\n87:         Configured requests.Session with HTTPAdapter mounted\n88:     \"\"\"\n89: ```\n90: \n91: **Implementation Details:**\n92: - Creates `requests.Session` instance\n93: - Mounts `HTTPAdapter` for both `http://` and `https://` schemes\n94: - Configures connection pooling with specified parameters\n95: - Returns session ready for use\n96: \n97: **Connection Pooling Benefits:**\n98: - Reuses TCP connections for multiple requests to same host\n99: - Reduces latency from TCP handshake and TLS negotiation\n100: - Limits resource usage with pool size constraints\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 1127. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-029: SDK HTTP 底层客户端 — Design\n\n## Overview\n\nThe SDK HTTP 底层客户端 provides the foundational HTTP client infrastructure for the AgentCube Python SDK, enabling communication with the Workload Manager (control plane) and Router (data plane) for Code Interpreter and Agent Runtime services.\n\n**Module:** `sdk-python`  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Source Root:** `/tmp/agentcube-ref/sdk-python/`  \n**Size:** M\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Components\n\n| Component | Location | Responsibility |\n|-----------|----------|----------------|\n| `create_session` | `agentcube/utils/http.py` | Creates pooled requests.Session with HTTPAdapter |\n| `read_token_from_file` | `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | Reads authentication token from file |\n| `get_logger` | `agentcube/utils/log.py` | Provides configured logger instances |","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/python-sdk/design.md","time":{"start":1775880444179,"end":1775880444197}}}}
